WHY ARE WE PAYING
80 BUCKS A POP

12:32.625 --> 12:34.834
TO SIT WHERE THEY
TELL US TO SIT,
EAT RUBBERY CHICKEN,

12:34.834 --> 12:35.792
AND LISTEN TO
A SPECIAL SELECTION

12:35.792 --> 12:38.250
OF BARBARA JOHNS'
FAVORITE TUNES

12:38.250 --> 12:40.333
WHEN WE CAN HOLD
THE ANTI-PROM?

12:40.333 --> 12:43.500
WHERE IT'S NOT
ABOUT WHO YOU BRING,
BUT WHO YOU ARE.

12:43.500 --> 12:44.750
I LIKE IT.

12:44.750 --> 12:47.166
