THIS IS MY RESTAURANT,

13:34.125 --> 13:35.542
SO I WILL BE HERE.

13:35.542 --> 13:36.208
AND EVERY PROM
NEEDS A CHAPERONE.

13:36.208 --> 13:39.208
OK.

13:39.208 --> 13:41.458
GREAT.

13:41.458 --> 13:44.041
