UNSCATHED.

13:49.834 --> 13:52.417
HE SAYS HE'S NUMB
AT THIS POINT.

13:52.417 --> 13:53.458
IS THAT A GOOD THING?

13:53.458 --> 13:54.917
I DON'T KNOW.

13:54.917 --> 13:57.333
BUT HE DID SEEM,
REMARKABLY ENOUGH,

13:57.333 --> 13:58.583
TOTALLY OK.

13:58.583 --> 14:01.000
WELL,
THAT'S A RELIEF.

14:02.291 --> 14:03.959
KIND OF GOT ME
TO THINKING, THOUGH.

14:03.959 --> 14:05.166
MMM!

14:05.166 --> 14:08.250
WHO PUT CAYENNE
PEPPER IN THIS
MARINARA SAUCE?

14:08.250 --> 14:10.166
