YEAH?

14:10.166 --> 14:13.667
I THOUGHT MAYBE WE
SHOULD DISCUSS WHAT
WE'RE DOING HERE?

14:13.667 --> 14:14.834
WHAT WE'RE DOING WHERE?

14:14.834 --> 14:17.166
THIS THING
