COULD ACTUALLY TURN OUT
TO BE A SUCCESS.

14:37.458 --> 14:39.834
Andie: IN A MANNER
OF SPEAKING. HI.

14:39.834 --> 14:43.500
JUST BECAUSE
THE DREGS OF SOCIETY
GO TO YOUR PROM

14:43.500 --> 14:45.041
DOES NOT MAKE IT
A SUCCESS.

14:45.041 --> 14:47.542
NOBODY THAT MATTERS
WOULD BE CAUGHT DEAD THERE.

14:47.542 --> 14:49.208
I CERTAINLY WOULDN'T
GO IF YOU PAID ME.

14:49.208 --> 14:51.166
GOOD THING,
'CAUSE WE DON'T
WANT YOUR KIND.

14:51.166 --> 14:54.333
AND WHAT KIND IS THAT,
THE GOOD CHRISTIAN KIND?

14:54.333 --> 14:55.250
[LAUGHS]

14:55.250 --> 14:58.333
