14:59.667 --> 15:03.834
THE INTOLERANT, JUDGMENTAL,
HYPOCRITICAL KIND.

15:03.834 --> 15:06.041
THE CLOSE-MINDED,
IMMATURE, BIGOTED KIND.

15:06.041 --> 15:07.208
