FASHION SENSE.

15:07.208 --> 15:08.208
REALLY BAD.

15:08.208 --> 15:10.625
LOOK, AT LEAST
I'M NOT GOING TO HELL.

15:11.917 --> 15:14.041
THAT'S IT? THAT'S
YOUR WHOLE COMEBACK?

15:14.041 --> 15:15.500
OOH!

15:15.500 --> 15:16.917
