A PRETTY GOOD COMEBACK.

15:16.917 --> 15:19.834
WELL, THAT THREAT
IS NOT YOURS TO MAKE.

15:19.834 --> 15:21.417
YOU JUST DON'T
GET IT, DO YOU?

15:21.417 --> 15:23.375
