IN THE BACKGROUND

15:40.834 --> 15:42.417
AND LET
YOUR WOMAN SHINE.

15:42.417 --> 15:46.625
OH, I THINK THAT HENRY
SHINES JUST FINE
ON HIS OWN, GRAMS.

15:46.625 --> 15:47.917
HE CERTAINLY DOES.

15:47.917 --> 15:49.041
[TEAPOT WHISTLES]

15:49.041 --> 15:51.834
OOH, THERE'S MY TEA.

15:51.834 --> 15:53.834
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

15:56.875 --> 16:00.291
