16:16.875 --> 16:19.625
OH, OK. TELL ME THAT
YOU WEREN'T THINKING

16:19.625 --> 16:21.041
THAT YOU, ME,
AND THE PROM DIDN'T MEAN

16:21.041 --> 16:23.000
THE DISTINCT POSSIBILITY

16:23.000 --> 16:26.375
