RENTED LIMO NOOKIE?

16:26.375 --> 16:28.667
I--I DIDN'T
RENT A LIMO.

16:28.667 --> 16:29.792
OK, THAT'S NOT
THE POINT.

16:29.792 --> 16:32.166
