DOING IT 15 MINUTES
BEFORE CURFEW,

16:35.417 --> 16:37.959
AND IT'S
COMPLETELY UNROMANTIC
AND WAY TOO FAST,

16:37.959 --> 16:42.166
AND IT--IT JUST
GENERALLY SUCKS.

16:42.166 --> 16:46.500
AND YOU CAN NEVER
TAKE THAT BACK OR
CHANGE IT, SO...

16:46.500 --> 16:50.083
SO I THOUGHT
THAT MAYBE WE COULD MAKE
THE DECISION RIGHT NOW

16:50.083 --> 16:52.208
NOT  TO DO IT.

16:52.208 --> 16:56.500
OH, UM,
I'M IN NO RACE.

16:56.500 --> 16:57.834
YOU KNOW THAT.

16:57.834 --> 16:59.583
OK.

17:01.166 --> 17:06.666
BUT WE...
WE ARE GONNA DO IT

17:06.666 --> 17:09.040
