17:27.541 --> 17:29.917
SO, UM, GUESS
YOU'RE PROBABLY GOING

17:29.917 --> 17:30.750
TO THAT WHOLE
ALTERNATIVE PROM THING.

17:30.750 --> 17:33.750
MM-HMM. OH, HO!

17:33.750 --> 17:34.875
YOU ARE NOT GONNA BELIEVE
WHAT I DID TODAY.

17:34.875 --> 17:37.542
I THREW MY TICKET BACK
IN BARBARA JOHNS' FACE.

17:37.542 --> 17:40.834
KNOW WHAT THAT WITCH SAID
TO ME WHEN I BOUGHT IT?

17:40.834 --> 17:43.125
"OH, THAT IS
SO BRAVE, ANDIE.

17:43.125 --> 17:45.708
A GIRL GOING
TO THE PROM ALONE."

17:45.708 --> 17:46.959
OOH!

17:46.959 --> 17:49.750
WHY WOULD YOU GO
TO THE PROM ALONE?

17:49.750 --> 17:50.542
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
SIFTING THROUGH OFFERS.

17:50.542 --> 17:54.041
YEAH.

17:54.041 --> 17:56.166
WELL, UH...

17:56.166 --> 17:58.834
