JUST TELL ME THAT?

18:03.417 --> 18:06.291
BECAUSE I DIDN'T WANT
A PITY ASK, OK?

18:06.291 --> 18:07.417
AND IT DOESN'T
MATTER ANYWAY,

18:07.417 --> 18:09.583
BECAUSE ALL OF MY FRIENDS
ARE GONNA BE THERE,

18:09.583 --> 18:11.500
AND AT THIS POINT,
I'M JUST GOING TO SUPPORT

18:11.500 --> 18:13.667
THE WHOLE STUPID
ALTERNATIVE PROM THING.

18:13.667 --> 18:15.083
