ABLE TO TELL ME.

18:15.083 --> 18:18.166
AND IT WOULDN'T BE
A PITY ASK,

18:18.166 --> 18:22.041
BECAUSE IT CAN'T BE PITY
IF IT'S AN HONOR.

18:23.250 --> 18:25.917
ANDREA McPHEE...

18:25.917 --> 18:28.667
WOULD YOU GO TO
THE PROM WITH ME?

18:31.583 --> 18:32.625
HI.

18:32.625 --> 18:34.583
HEY.

18:34.583 --> 18:35.667
SO...

18:35.667 --> 18:36.625
HEY.

18:36.625 --> 18:38.959
Dawson: WOW.

18:38.959 --> 18:41.583
YOU LOOK...

18:41.583 --> 18:44.417
IT'S JUST A DRESS,
DAWSON.

18:44.417 --> 18:46.000
Bessie:
OK, PICTURE TIME!

18:49.208 --> 18:50.333
[GIGGLES]

18:50.333 --> 18:51.500
