NO CORSAGES--

19:02.750 --> 19:04.542
BUT I HAD TO BRING
SOMETHING.

19:04.542 --> 19:07.834
SO I THOUGHT
I'D BRING THESE.

19:07.834 --> 19:09.667
DIAMOND EARRINGS?

19:09.667 --> 19:11.083
Bessie: WOW.

19:11.083 --> 19:12.959
DAWSON, I CAN'T
TAKE THESE.

19:12.959 --> 19:15.375
RELAX, THEY'RE MY MOM'S.

19:15.375 --> 19:18.208
THEY'RE ON LOAN, LIKE
AT THE ACADEMY AWARDS.

19:18.208 --> 19:19.917
I THOUGHT THEY WOULD
LOOK AMAZING ON YOU.

19:19.917 --> 19:23.333
I--I CAN'T WEAR THEM.
WHAT IF SOMETHING HAPPENS?

19:23.333 --> 19:26.917
