TO WHAT, YOUR EARLOBES?

19:26.917 --> 19:28.333
STOP IT. PUT 'EM ON.

19:30.667 --> 19:32.041
THEY ARE BEAUTIFUL.

19:32.041 --> 19:34.041
SO PUT THEM ON,
AND I'LL GET
ONE MORE PICTURE.

19:40.834 --> 19:44.625
Bessie: OHH.

19:44.625 --> 19:46.250
THANK YOU.

19:47.125 --> 19:50.208
1...2...3!

19:56.166 --> 19:56.834
Gale: HI. HI.

19:56.834 --> 19:57.834
Mitch: WELCOME.

19:57.834 --> 20:01.417
[SIGHS] OH, BOY.

20:01.417 --> 20:03.000
INTERESTING CROWD.

20:03.000 --> 20:03.667
LOCK THE CASH REGISTER.

20:03.667 --> 20:06.208
I'M ON IT.

20:10.542 --> 20:13.250
HEY, CAN YOU BELIEVE
WE WORE THE SAME THING?

20:13.250 --> 20:15.750
[LAUGHS]

20:15.750 --> 20:19.542
YEAH, WELL, I THOUGHT
IT WAS PRETTY FUNNY.

20:19.542 --> 20:21.875
[SIGHS]

20:21.875 --> 20:23.792
JACK, I'M NOT EXPECTING
YOU TO DANCE WITH ME,

20:23.792 --> 20:24.792
