HEY.

20:36.041 --> 20:37.625
HEY.

20:37.625 --> 20:39.375
HEY, JACK, ETHAN.

20:42.959 --> 20:44.500
HEY, YOU GUYS.

20:44.500 --> 20:46.500
JOEY, I LOVE
THOSE EARRINGS.

20:46.500 --> 20:48.458
