[LAUGHS] THANKS.

21:16.917 --> 21:17.875
HEY, ETHAN.

21:17.875 --> 21:20.083
Ethan: HI, ANDIE.

21:20.083 --> 21:20.583
HENRY.
HEY.

21:46.875 --> 21:49.458
SO, HERE WE ARE.

21:49.458 --> 21:49.959
YEP.

21:49.959 --> 21:53.291
AT THE PROM.

21:53.291 --> 21:53.500
YEP.

21:55.959 --> 21:58.500
SO, WHAT ARE YOU
THINKING?

21:58.500 --> 22:00.542
I WASN'T THINKING
ABOUT SEX, OK?

22:00.542 --> 22:05.000
