YOU'RE ALLOWED
TO THINK ABOUT SEX.

22:05.000 --> 22:08.625
WELL, I--I WASN'T.

22:08.625 --> 22:10.125
NO, I'M SURE.

22:10.125 --> 22:12.542
I'M JUST SAYING
IF YOU WERE,
IT'S FINE.

22:12.542 --> 22:14.625
YOU CAN THINK ABOUT SEX,
I CAN THINK ABOUT SEX,

22:14.625 --> 22:18.417
IT'S JUST THAT TONIGHT
THAT IT'S NOT A FACTOR.

22:18.417 --> 22:20.208
RIGHT?

22:25.667 --> 22:27.792
I'M GLAD, YOU KNOW.

22:27.792 --> 22:29.333
ABOUT WHAT?

22:29.333 --> 22:31.792
THAT YOU HAD THE COURAGE
TO BRING ME, JACK.

22:31.792 --> 22:34.166
I KNOW IT'S NOT EASY.
EVEN FOR ME.

22:34.166 --> 22:36.667
WHEN BRAD AND I
FIRST TOLD PEOPLE
WHAT WAS HAPPENING--

22:36.667 --> 22:38.208
