WITH A LOT OF SOLACE
RIGHT NOW.

22:44.708 --> 22:46.667
WHAT I WAS GONNA SAY,
JACK,

22:46.667 --> 22:49.625
IS THAT BRAD AND I
NEVER DID ANYTHING
TOGETHER.

22:49.625 --> 22:50.875
IN FACT,
FOR ALL MY BRAVADO,

22:50.875 --> 22:53.750
I'VE NEVER ASKED A GUY
TO ANYTHING LIKE THIS.

22:53.750 --> 22:56.333
WHA...

22:56.333 --> 22:59.250
YOU MEAN ALL THAT CRAP
ABOUT ACTUALIZATION,

22:59.250 --> 23:01.166
YOU'VE NEVER ACTUALIZED?

23:01.166 --> 23:03.208
I GUESS I THOUGHT
IT WAS A HURDLE

23:03.208 --> 23:04.708
WE COULD JUMP OVER
TOGETHER.

23:04.708 --> 23:06.208
