IS THAT, ETHAN?

23:10.208 --> 23:11.708
SO YOU WIN IN
THE COURAGE DEPARTMENT.

23:11.708 --> 23:14.041
NO, I DON'T, BECAUSE
I WAS TRICKED INTO IT.

23:14.041 --> 23:16.041
