TO BE HERE RIGHT NOW.

23:20.542 --> 23:21.792
WELL, I'M SORRY.

23:21.792 --> 23:22.708
SO AM I.

23:22.708 --> 23:24.375
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

23:24.375 --> 23:25.542
I'M GOING
TO GET A SODA.

23:25.542 --> 23:29.125
I WAS WONDERING,
WISE GAY SAGE
THAT YOU ARE,

23:29.125 --> 23:33.375
COKE, DIET PEPSI--
WHAT'S BETTER FOR
MY SELF-ACTUALIZATION?

23:38.208 --> 23:41.250
YOU KNOW,
THERE ARE OTHER THINGS
THAT WE CAN TALK ABOUT.

23:41.250 --> 23:43.583
BESIDES SEX.

23:43.583 --> 23:45.208
OF COURSE.

23:45.208 --> 23:46.625
WE--WE COULD
TALK ABOUT...

23:49.542 --> 23:51.583
SUMMER.
WE COULD TALK ABOUT

23:51.583 --> 23:53.583
WHAT WE'RE GONNA
DO THIS SUMMER.

23:53.583 --> 23:55.000
I THOUGHT WE COULD TAKE
A COUPLE OF DAY TRIPS

23:55.000 --> 23:56.208
UP TO NANTUCKET,

23:56.208 --> 23:57.834
GO SEE SOME CONCERTS
UP IN BOSTON--

23:57.834 --> 24:00.792
SURE. WHEN I GET BACK
FROM FOOTBALL CAMP.

24:00.792 --> 24:02.583
WHAT-BALL CAMP?

24:02.583 --> 24:05.000
