THAT RUINS THE NIGHT.

24:21.291 --> 24:23.667
I'VE RUINED THE NIGHT?

24:23.667 --> 24:26.166
AND AS FOR LATER GOES,
WHATEVER SLIM
POSSIBILITY

24:26.166 --> 24:28.250
MAY HAVE EXISTED
THAT YOU AND I MIGHT
ACTUALLY HAVE SEX,

24:28.250 --> 24:29.625
YOU CAN JUST FORGET
ABOUT THAT NOW.

24:29.625 --> 24:32.291
WE ALREADY ESTABLISHED
WE WEREN'T GONNA HAVE
SEX TONIGHT.

24:32.291 --> 24:33.834
COME ON, HENRY.
THAT'S JUST WHAT YOU SAY

24:33.834 --> 24:36.750
TO ALLEVIATE
THE PRESSURE AND MAKE
IT SEEM SPONTANEOUS.

24:36.750 --> 24:38.041
